stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Spawning

    Spawning --> Normal : Spawn Complete

    Normal --> Moving : Has Input Direction
    Moving --> Normal : No Valid Movement

    Moving --> Eating : Collision with Pellet
    Eating --> Moving : Pellet Consumed

    Moving --> PoweredUp : Collision with Power Pellet
    PoweredUp --> Moving : Power Duration Ends

    PoweredUp --> Eating : Collision with Pellet
    Eating --> PoweredUp : Still Powered

    PoweredUp --> ChaseGhost : Collision with Frightened Ghost
    ChaseGhost --> PoweredUp : Ghost Eaten

    Moving --> Dying : Collision with Normal Ghost
    PoweredUp --> Dying : Collision with Normal Ghost
    Normal --> Dying : Collision with Normal Ghost

    Dying --> Dead : Death Animation Complete
    Dead --> Spawning : Respawn (Lives > 0)
    Dead --> [*] : Game Over (Lives = 0)
